Maxwell

Tamno sivi sfinks maak, Sebastianov familiar.

esto je mrzovoljan, ini se da naroito ne voli Sebastiana.

Redovito umire u borbama. Iskreno, ne sjeam se je li preivio iti jednu do sada.

ini se da Maxwell ima sposobnost odbiti pojaviti se. Sebastian je podijelio priu o jednom tulumu na faksu koji je otiao malo predaleko i tokom kojeg je Maxwell bio sluajno zapaljen. Nakon toga se maak po prvi put odbio vratiti.

Kasnije je znao i sam upadati u pogibeljne nevolje, vrljajui gradom.

Pomae Sebastianu nositi se s njegovom boleu.

Super Maxwell

Maxwellov dnevnik

Day 225, Year 5062

Dear Diary,

Ah, the life of a familiar is never dull, especially when you're a cat like me, Maxwell, in the service of Sebastian, a wizard whose idea of fun is, well, questionable. Today, for instance, he sent me to "play" with zombies. Zombies! Of all the absurd things!

Now, I fancy myself quite the agile feline, but those lumbering, groaning masses are deceptively grabby. I tried my usual repertoire of swipes and feints, but alas, one of them managed to catch me. It was rather embarrassing, really. There I was, Maxwell, the sleek and cunning, being bested by a creature with the coordination of a drunken ogre.

Day 227, Year 5062

Dear Diary,

You would not believe the audacity! Just when I thought Sebastian couldn't top his previous shenanigans, he sends me back to those dreadful zombies. Yes, again! It's like he thinks I have unlimited lives or something. Spoiler alert: I don't.

Needless to say, my second foray among the undead was as short-lived as the first. Those zombies might be slow, but they're rather persistent. Once again, I found myself back from the brink, thanks to Sebastian's magic.

I've decided it's time for some well-deserved payback. Tonight, as he sleeps, his beloved robe will be enchanted to belt out the most annoying bard songs at the top of its threads. Let's see how he likes being disturbed.

Furiously yours, Maxwell, the Twice-Tormented, Plotter of Revenge

Day 251, Year 5062

Dear Diary,

I heard something from the weird hole in the wall, like it wants to crawl out... Its fascinating. Sebastian left 3 hours ago, probably forgot about me. Thank god. I like this hole. I will guard this hole.
